cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with computation tree logic (CTL) and its expressiveness using possibility measures. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses model checking of linear-time properties with uncertain information, which is a common problem in AI. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper discusses a method to solve the PoCTL model-checking problem, which is relevant to software verification and testing. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with the expressiveness of PoCTL and its equivalent expressions of basic CTL formulae. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the time complexity of the PoCTL model-checking method.
